OL,3,C'The chippy should be a treat, but
OL,4,Cpeople need to be able to afford it'
OL,6,FA chip shop in Runcorn is asking for
OL,7,Fmore help for small businesses in the
OL,8,Frun up to the budget this week.
OL,10,FNeptune Fish Bar has been in the
OL,11,Fcentre of Runcorn for around 20 years,
OL,12,Fand has managed to withstand changes
OL,13,Fto the economy.
OL,15,FThe manager, Graham Stapleton, said
OL,16,Fthe town's hospitality industry has
OL,17,F"declined with the cost of living" as
OL,18,F"people just haven't got the money."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
