OL,6,FThis will be the first budget since
OL,7,Fthe Runcorn and Helsby by-election
OL,8,Fwhen voters chose Reform UK over
OL,9,FLabour.
OL,11,FIn May, Sarah Pochin overturned a
OL,12,FLabour majority of nearly 15,000 in
OL,13,Fthe Cheshire constituency, making her
OL,14,Fthe first Reform MP in the North West
OL,15,Fof England.
OL,17,FShe by just six votes following a
OL,18,Frecount on 1 May 2025.
