OL,6,FThe by-election was triggered when
OL,7,Fformer Labour MP Mike Amesbury quit
OL,8,Fafter admitting to punching a
OL,9,Fconstituent.
OL,11,FOn the streets of Runcorn, voters told
OL,12,FITV News that they need to feel better
OL,13,Foff before they can believe in
OL,14,Fmainstream politics again.
OL,16,F"Unless they do something for the low-
OL,17,Fpaid people, the ones who are on the
OL,18,Fstreets, we're not going to get
OL,19,Fanywhere" said one.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
