OL,3,C'The chippy should be a treat, but
OL,4,Cpeople need to be able to afford it'
OL,6,FHe said: "The value of the potatoes
OL,7,Fthat's sat in the shed is around
OL,8,F#80,000 that should be in my bank
OL,9,Faccount.
OL,11,F"If they want to import everything and
OL,12,Fclose the door on agriculture in this
OL,13,Fcountry then tell us and do it now.
OL,15,F"They can't keep just using us as a
OL,16,Fbackup: 'If we can't get it from
OL,17,Fanywhere else, we've got our own, but
OL,18,Fif we can buy it somewhere cheaper,
OL,19,Fwe'll buy it somewhere cheaper.'
