OL,3,C'The chippy should be a treat, but
OL,4,Cpeople need to be able to afford it'
OL,6,F"And that's what the Government have
OL,7,Fgot to stop now."
OL,9,FMinisters insist the budget will bring
OL,10,Fdown the cost of living.
OL,12,FBusiness Secretary, Peter Kyle MP,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are a Government that acts
OL,14,Fin the interests of business, of the
OL,15,Fpeople who work for business, and for
OL,16,Fthe overall economic growth that means
OL,17,Fthat people can look forward to a
OL,18,Fbetter life into the future than the
OL,19,Fone they're having today."
