OL,6,FAcross Runcorn the challenges facing
OL,7,Fthis Government are clear.
OL,9,FThe Chancellor's promised a fair plan
OL,10,Fto tackle them but, with Labour's
OL,11,Fpolitical grip on the North West
OL,12,Fstarting to slip, the stakes are high
OL,13,Fand rising higher.
